item.description: Contacting me If you have any questions about any of my posts please don’t hesitate in commenting using Disqus. If you’d like to get in contact with me casually to discuss any topics noted in this blog you can totally reach me on Twitter (check out my Twitter profile in the sidebar). If you would like to contact me professionally feel free to jump onto my LinkedIn profile (sidebar) and get in touch.
